Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================Pre===================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.04,0:00:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 哪天办结婚典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等有钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥和这种穷小子结婚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么直白 爸爸我会伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起我就叫你「爸爸」了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别 好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事实上就是岳父了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我就叫你「儿子」好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啊爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================OP===================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:03.77,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}熟悉的坡道上 却已不见你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:09.45,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}柔和的阳光 透过树叶投下斑点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.53,0:01:14.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}我独自一人 伫立在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:21.99,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}回顾着那些 温暖的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:30.11,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}只有你 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.18,0:01:36.18,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}在变幻的时间中 永驻我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:43.95,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}风吹而过 泪水渗眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:50.99,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}你的身影 已变得更远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:53.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}任何时候都不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:55.27,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}哪怕一切的一切全部改变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:57.48,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}不忘记那一件 那一件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:01:59.86,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}稀松平常之事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:00.97,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}终会让你看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:04.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}那被光芒包裹着的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:06.25,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}守护 守护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:09.29,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\be1}直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================Text===================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候应该说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么…是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始 就是两个人生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说「预备 开始」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟没有终点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一说 也的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此要两人相互支撑着前行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是「请多关照」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时我还想立下誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓言？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我冈崎渚不会再哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管如何艰辛 都会努力克服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 高兴时可能还是会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是如此不济的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还请多多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先洗澡真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天换我先洗就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 那我先用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚洗澡的声音 住那边时不就经常听么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 因为水一下子喷出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等一会儿才会变温水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始时一点点拧开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我会尽快洗好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 慢慢洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君明天还要干活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要早点睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天开始也会去找工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找个工作 我不能一个人闲着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚 醒着么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 醒着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要工作…是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然家务也不会马虎的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家务我也会分担啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身体不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然身体柔弱 但不想整个人都一直柔弱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 好像我又任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从来没提过什么要求吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是拜托朋也君做各种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪大叔打棒球 一起牵个手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此之类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 就想牵个手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是夫妇了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后会发生很多事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或有忙乱辛酸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和朋也君一起 就能坦然面对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 和你在一起就觉得不会输给任何事物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 要一直留在我身边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直留在朋也君身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 我和渚的生活开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起就要撑起二人家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这对我来说谈不上痛苦 而是愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作结束 我就直接回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回渚守候着的家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回属于两人的家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天给仁科同学打了个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业典礼时她给了我号码
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在是在复读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 为了进音乐学校而努力学习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说为了减轻父母的负担 要自己打工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁科同学说是要在下月开张的一家餐馆打工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还问我「要不要做个伴」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当服务员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好也在找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得正合适
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 比起尽是陌生人的工作来更让人放心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要先跟大叔和早苗说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君 在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想以前宫泽说过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小镇有个古老的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「光」会出现在幸福的人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想 说不定现在的我们身边就有「光」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说拿到「光」就能实现愿望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会许什么愿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…有个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来就帮你买
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你小子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下班早 空出时间来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就过来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我这几天都在等着这一刻的到来也不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看正在工作的渚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大男人独自去餐厅 凄凉地吃巧克力圣代之类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很不像样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说为啥是巧克力圣代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没去过渚打工的那餐厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想看看她的服务员装束吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果老爸特地过去拍照这种事传出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被邻里笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就重新包装为你的友人甲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事马上就会暴露吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知情的人看了只会以为是谜之RAPPER吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YO!YO!我是MC秋生!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿起麦克风就是最强的面包师！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是在自爆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的那是真的吗！真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BROTHER喂 等等我！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里以前是片林子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长好多树
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊 变得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无名RAPPER的YO！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理惠 店长正看着这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热闹是好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块地方的变化会越来越大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 刚才起就一脸不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…偶然空出了点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就来看看你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听仁科和杉坂同学说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是初次见面…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是菜单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢慢过目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 没暴露吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有其父必有其女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵 别这么夸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以点单了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要热咖啡 这边的是圣代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要最大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热咖啡一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和巧克力＆草莓MIX圣代钻石特别版是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥我要吃这么时髦的玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要吃圣代的么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过这样的话么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了 很清楚地说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古河同学很有人气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:14:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有客人就是冲着她过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理惠 不是古河同学了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冈崎渚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是制服魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确显得更可爱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理惠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 打工啥时候结束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭我请 一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我得直接回家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我回去工作了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧…是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…请等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 不会添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几年不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这里碰见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给其他客人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟老子到外头说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不会来这店了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 给跑掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长请两位过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦事就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜噗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们多事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我很高兴得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 想到朋也君要被店长训…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我夫人这件事我不会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您夫人干得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经暴露了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是听仁科和杉坂说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有这机会 就想打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 心爱的夫人被纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您心里自然不好受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实之前也有过类似的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那时她就处理得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理得很好…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体柔弱 好像也没有工作经验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是个聪明而坚强的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对敝店来说是不可或缺的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为太过认真 所以失败时会很消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点请在家里好好抚慰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 让您费了这么多心思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…呃 内人就继续有劳您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敝人才是 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也找到了新的居所了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不禁想起在演剧社的日子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某朋友甲也说很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点也不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁科和杉坂同学才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起之前仁科同学说的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说学校会建新楼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧楼好像会推掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年后入学的新生 都能在崭新的教室学习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什么好事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎会是好事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗 朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像没什么的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说错了话 应该道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么生气了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是生气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是动摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看…不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演剧社的活动室在旧楼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是一起努力过来的回忆的场所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那栋楼没了 会很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…有点那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像有点神经质了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想得不周全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真是不像样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么会如此不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小镇在不断改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和渚周围的环境
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我们本身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到所有事物都改变了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 还会继续喜欢这个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 终于洗出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候拍了这么多啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后去了好几趟 去拍女儿的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费了番工夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时而伏在地板上 时而藏身厨房之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求杂技才能拍到的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你能不被赶出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女的都上哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想给她们展示下我的伟业呐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…渚说有事要和早苗谈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 话说要给她们看这照片么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点想吐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 莫非有小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太轻率了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 你要是有那能耐早就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像真的有了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是渚和朋也的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊早苗！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有孩子是怎么回事…鸿雁授子么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是从白菜地里捡来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和朋也君是夫妇 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这家伙会说么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H的事情也做过了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在双亲面前直白地说这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球上也很难再找到这等生物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚真厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月经也停了 应该没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可喜可贺啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多 多谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================ED===================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:26.47,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}双眼凝视着 流动的云朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.64,0:22:33.39,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}心中感受着 天空变幻的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:41.58,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}伫立不前的我们 察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:48.60,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}这变迁的世界编织出的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:55.84,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}伸出的指尖 不断寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:23:04.53,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那恒久不变的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:12.09,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起的手中火炬闪亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:19.82,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那是通向明天的小小路标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:27.15,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}现在也在不断回响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:34.68,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那一天的话语 终将化为誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.83,0:23:39.44,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)}推动我前行
